# an — manual request examples
# Copy to an.http, fill in the placeholders, use a REST client
# (VS Code REST Client, IntelliJ) to execute.
#
# @API_KEY = your bootstrap or tenant api key
# @TENANT = default

### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### JWKS (public signing keys, no api key needed)
GET http://localhost:8080/.well-known/jwks.json

### Register an account (returns the verification token — deliver it yourself)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "password": "password-1"}

### Verify
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/verify
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "verificationToken": "<from register>"}

### Resend verification (regenerates the token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/verify/resend
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com"}

### Password logon
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "clientId": "phone", "password": "password-1"}

### Acknowledge the token pair (required before validate/renew)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/ack
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "accessToken": "<access>", "refreshToken": "<refresh>"}

### Validate an access token (signature + expiry + acknowledged session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/validate
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "accessToken": "<access>"}

### Renew (rotates the refresh token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/renew
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "refreshToken": "<refresh>"}

### Revoke one client (empty clientId revokes all)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/revoke
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "clientId": "phone"}

### Request a magic logon code (returns the code — deliver it yourself)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/code/request
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com"}

### Logon with the code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/code
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "clientId": "phone", "code": "123456"}

### Google social logon
POST http://localhost:8080/api/authenticate/social
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "provider": "google", "idToken": "<google id token>", "clientId": "phone"}

### Forgot password (returns the reset token — deliver it yourself)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/forgot
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com"}

### Reset password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/reset
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "resetToken": "<from forgot>", "newPassword": "password-2"}

### Change password
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/password
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com", "currentPassword": "password-1", "newPassword": "password-2"}

### Delete account (soft)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/delete
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "email": "user@example.com"}

### Create a tenant-scoped api key (bootstrap key only; secret shown once)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/apikeys
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "name": "my-service"}

### List api keys (bootstrap key only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/apikeys/list
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}"}

### Revoke an api key (bootstrap key only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/apikeys/delete
Content-Type: application/json
X-AN-API-KEY: {{API_KEY}}

{"tenantId": "{{TENANT}}", "id": "<key id>"}
